Davion Navar Henry Only has been adopted by his old case worker Connie Bell Going . 
  Davion was adopted by a minister in Ohio but sent back to Florida after he fought with one of the minister's children . 
  In 2013 Davion made a plea in front of a church congregation for a family to 'love him forever' Davion has been in the foster care system since he was born . 
  Last July he called his former case worker and asked her to adopt him . 
  He has now been officially adopted by Connie and her family . 
 